Asari Dokubo has slammed the leader of the Indigenous People of Biafra (IPOB), Nnamdi Kanu for declaring Biafra a Jewish Nation and threatening to kill all followers of other religions. In a video sourced from the Nation,Asari Dokubo described Kanu as an “idiot.” READ ALSO “WHY NATIONS FAIL” PART I He lamented that the IPOB leader only knows how to rant on frivolous issues instead of uniting with other agitators to make Biafra a reality. See video here;